<br>
To do this when you need to, just hold the Shift key, and press the minus key as many times as needed until you can move smoothly - there is a minimum setting - you'll see that after a certain number of presses it doesnt have any further effect. <br>
<br>
To extend your clip plane / range of vision, press shift and hit the + key, till it maxes out again. I use that all the time when going from empty zones to busy ones. For instance when entering the bazaar, I reduce my clip plane down quite low, so that its not laggy for me to use the bank, merchants, etc.<br>
<br>
Dont forget to increase the clip plane later, as you may forget and go around with reduced visibility range for some time before remembering :P<br>
<br>
