<br>
A good rule of thumb, when you're exploring while invisible, is to take your time and /consider a mob before you get too close.  If it says &quot;Regards you indifferently&quot; (doesn't matter what color of a con), then it doesn't see through.<br>
<br>
There is an invisibility vs. undead spell, but living mobs will see you and you can't have Invisibility and Invisibility vs Undead on you at the same time. <p>Tadwen Brytewisp<br>
Lvl 55 Outrider<br>
